      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771498425173,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Divides data into non overlaping subsets(cluster)\nEach object belong to exactly one cluster.\nIt requires the no of cluster to be specified in advanced",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Divides data into non overlaping subsets(cluster)\nEach object belong to exactly one cluster.\nIt requires the no of cluster to be specified in advanced",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "F90ITXkZsgWFlY2KK72w6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 346,
      "y": 1204,
      "width": 527.259521484375,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5G",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 397205531,
      "version": 138,
      "versionNonce": 1582383003,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771498662190,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "It builds a hierarchy of clusters and represented as a\ndendrogram\nIt doesnt requires the no of clusters in advance",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "It builds a hierarchy of clusters and represented as a\ndendrogram\nIt doesnt requires the no of clusters in advance",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "FIyMBKKsxTy3CzHgsGWJn",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 312,
      "y": 1326,
      "width": 550.1195068359375,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5H",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1112211835,
      "version": 163,
      "versionNonce": 1307820731,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771498777405,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "It forms clusters based on dense region of data points.\nIt can discover clusters of arbitary shape.\nIt can identify outliers as noise",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "It forms clusters based on dense region of data points.\nIt can discover clusters of arbitary shape.\nIt can identify outliers as noise",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "0_9zWW7cI1mAkcAySrEit",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1185.30078125,
      "y": 1081.453125,
      "width": 579.1195068359375,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5I",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 601936533,
      "version": 339,
      "versionNonce": 672620373,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771498938830,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Strengths:\n    fast and effienct for large dataset\n    provides clear cluster assignments\n\nWeakness:\n    it requires the no of clusters to be specified in advance\n    sensitive to inital centroid\n    sensitive to outliers and noise\n    may converge to local minimum instead of global optimum",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Strengths:\n    fast and effienct for large dataset\n    provides clear cluster assignments\n\nWeakness:\n    it requires the no of clusters to be specified in advance\n    sensitive to inital centroid\n    sensitive to outliers and noise\n    may converge to local minimum instead of global optimum",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "vOQPLxu3KnyVsHaRNpNrL",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1187.30078125,
      "y": 1332.453125,
      "width": 657.2393798828125,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5J",
